latestPosts.caption: recently i’ve been living offline, despite my job which requires me to share my latest work online. instagram has felt weird lately but i can still make my page mean something to me and those of you on here. with the world changing so much and even our own friends and family dynamics shifting beyond normalcy, ive been holding my loved ones closer more than ever because they are ultimately all i have. my life has changed so much in the last year; change is definitely very scary but staying the same is worse.
